ji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實啲老母成日話可以讀書自己交學費<br />\n係啲人借左政府錢咋？<br />\n讀緊書返pt揾3,4千個月有乜可能學費+生活費自己負擔到哂"},{"pid":"99819b4bd1ad4d0ecc6aae5a55afdb05b139d9b7","tid":194822,"uid":33345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:31:12.000Z","msg":"呀媽好少會激嬲我 反而老豆以為讀過吓書乜都識<br />\n電腦電話有咩唔識 即刻問我<br />\n我話我都唔識<br />\n佢一句車埋嚟：有無搞錯呀，讀杘片㗎？<br />\n男朋友讀cs 老豆有時又會問佢一啲電腦硬件上嘅嘢<br />\n佢又會話：唔係讀電腦嘅咩，呢啲都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a33e71dae8636286f2c1234c99a723ebc51e81b","tid":194822,"uid":89449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:35:52.000Z","msg":"咁叻，你煮囉"},{"pid":"4ff6aee458be249707d510b27a53a13c85bee9fd","tid":194822,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:40:44.000Z","msg":"你大佬之前讀書都係自己掙錢交學費，好心你返工就唔好亂洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲錢比你大嫂儲起佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係返學就返工，我啲錢都係用黎食飯搭車，最多都買多件衫。<br />\n我唔撚係細路仔，你鍾意比晒啲錢比佢儲係你嘅事，唔好格硬要我學你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日撚日都係講同樣嘅野，屌完你第日又講返同樣嘅野，真係屌你都嘥鳩氣"},{"pid":"41510350e024ceed3b1b3337b8935c96134a4c48","tid":194822,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:56:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個個俾家用養全家話我淨係識食同訓<br />\n但佢連家務都冇做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個個<span style=\"color: red;\">月</span>俾家用養全家話我淨係識食同<span style=\"color: red;\">痾</span><br />\n但佢連家務都冇做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你癈啫，唔比家用咪得囉"},{"pid":"b956c77468525ba62bd37824bc478085a21a96a6","tid":194822,"uid":81709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0